    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093600/extras/5626bf09720b740b95afeb3e3d85a34d.poster.avif?t=1743863713\" width=596 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093600/extras/5626bf09720b740b95afeb3e3d85a34d.webm?t=1743863713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093600/extras/5626bf09720b740b95afeb3e3d85a34d.mp4?t=1743863713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Freed by the shockwaves of a dangerous threat, you, <i>Project ZZ</i>, have to traverse a cyberpunk world, battle your way through waves of <i>Projects</i>, and face <i>Project E-Dog</i> head on!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2>Project ZipZap is a fast-paced, speedrunner friendly, hack and dash game that incentivises skill expression and rewards mastery of game mechanics. Featuring:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Fast-paced movement-based combat: Dash to evade, and dash back to destroy.<br></li><li> Five hand-crafted levels including an explosive boss battle.<br></li><li> Three different dashes, each with special abilities, ultimates and interactions.<br></li><li> Achieve mastery by speedrunning levels and getting a high rank during combat.<br></li><li> Compete against players and friends on the leaderboards, and stay competitive by racing their ghosts.</li></ul><br><i>Project ZipZap was developed as a final year university project over the course of seven months by eleven developers.</i>",
